text: Abasese tara tara prati mithyaropa karala; phale amara take o tara sange yara naukate chila taderake najata dilama ebam taderake sthalabhisikta kari. Ara yara amadera ayatasamuhe mithyaropa karechila taderake nimajjita karalama. Kaje'i dekhuna, yaderake satarka kara hayechila tadera parinama ki hayechila
